            <p class="mb-4">
              But you know: PC350s run 15,000-20,000 hours. This one has 5,000+ productive hours left.
            </p>

            <p class="mb-4">
              More importantly: Every hour it works is revenue YOU keep instead of writing checks to subcontractors.
            </p>

            <p class="mb-4 font-bold">
              We approve equipment 10+ years old.
            </p>

            <p class="mb-4">
              Your quarry. Your excavator. Your margins.
            </p>

            <p class="mb-4">
              Every cubic meter you excavate yourself is profit that stays in YOUR business.
            </p>

            <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-500 p-6 my-6">
              <p class="font-bold text-green-800 text-xl mb-3">0% deposit available. Equipment 10+ years old accepted. Quarry operators welcome.</p>
              <p class="text-gray-800 mb-2">Keep excavation revenue in-house.</p>
              <p class="text-gray-800 mb-2">Build your quarry's capability.</p>
              <p class="text-gray-800 font-semibold mt-4">Control every stage of production.</p>
            </div>

            <p class="text-xl font-bold text-[#8B6F47]">
